&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zez86zz122zz80zz81zz70zz82zz74zvfz72zz85zvsz77zz68zk2z71z0z88z2z75z2z77zvz75ziu&quot;&gt;Experience developing and debugging production services in C++, Go, or Rust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zfwz66zwhdz68zz78zz74zl2vz70z03z66zz80zrz77zt56z90zz81zz74zz69zpz80zkf&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz86zez86zz122zz80zz81zz70zz82zz74zvfz72zz85zvsz77zz68zk2z71z0z88z2z75z2z77zvz75ziu&quot;&gt;Familiarity with distributed storage systems, file systems, or data infrastructure at scale&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zfwz66zwhdz68zz78zz74zl2vz70z03z66zz80zrz77zt56z90zz81zz74zz69zpz80zkf&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
